               stealing, on the <rs id="t18310908-116-cd633" type="crimeDate">16th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-116-off632 t18310908-116-cd633"></join>, 1 waistcoat, value 6d.; 2 handkerchiefs, value 1s., and 3 towels, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18310908-116-victim987" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Grogan
                  <interp inst="t18310908-116-victim987" type="surname" value="Grogan"></interp>
