                  </persName>
            . I lodge in Bull's-Head-yard. On Saturday, the 16th of July, I saw the prisoner take a bundle of things into the opposite room.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-116-person990">
                  AUGUSTUS 
                  HORNCASTLE
               <interp inst="t18310908-116-person990" type="surname" value="HORNCASTLE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-116-person990" type="given" value="AUGUSTUS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-116-person990" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Policeman. I took the prisoner on Sunday, the 17th of July, in the room; I found this knife on him.</p>
               <p>CHARLOTTE GROGAN. It was a knife of that description he pulled out.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. That knife was never in my possession - I never gave her a blow.</p>
               <p>
